\title{the indicator function of a subset}
\date{2024-01-25}
\author{jonmsterling}
\contributor{marcelofiore}
\taxon{definition}
\import{jms-00JB}

\p{The \dem{indicator function} or \dem{characteristic function} of #{S\subseteq A} is defined to be the [predicate](jms-00LO) #{\chi_S\colon A\to \brk{2}} defined piecewise below:}
##{
 \chi_S\prn{a} = \begin{cases}
  1 & \text{if } a \in S\\
  0 & \text{if } a \not\in S
 \end{cases}
}